---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy - Leaders In Incentives, Rewards & Loyalty Programs | GRG India"
  description="Read GRG India's privacy policy to understand how we collect, use, and protect your personal information."
  canonical="https://www.grgindia.in/privacy-policy/"
>
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <div class="prose prose-lg text-gray-700 space-y-6">
        <p>
          Tajonline India Private Limited ("My Incentives") is concerned about your privacy. Please read the following to learn more about our Privacy Policy. This Privacy Policy is in accordance with the Indian Information Technology Act, 2000 and the Information Technology (Reasonable Security and Procedures and Sensitive Personal Data or Information) Rules, 2011 prescribed thereunder ("Applicable Law") and is intended to provide you with clear and complete information about the treatment of your Personally Identifiable Data and Information and your Sensitive Personal Data or Information that My Incentives collects in connection with the Services offered on our website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Personally Identifiable Information</h2>
        <p>
          "Personally Identifiable Information" means any information that relates to a natural person, which, either directly or indirectly, in combination with other information available or likely to be available with My Incentives, is capable of identifying such person. This includes your name, age, gender, address, telephone number, and any other personal information we collect.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Sensitive Personal Data or Information</h2>
        <p>For the purposes of our Services, "Sensitive Personal Data or Information" means Personal Information consisting of:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Passwords</li>
          <li>Financial information such as bank account, credit card or debit card or other payment instrument details</li>
          <li>Physical, physiological and mental health condition</li>
          <li>Sexual orientation</li>
          <li>Medical records and history</li>
          <li>Biometric information</li>
          <li>Any detail relating to the above clauses as provided to a body corporate for providing services</li>
          <li>Any of the information received under the above clauses by a body corporate for processing, stored or processed under lawful contract or otherwise</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
          Any information that is freely available or accessible in the public domain or furnished under the Right to Information Act, 2005 or any other law for the time being in force shall not be regarded as Sensitive Personal Data or Information.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Consent</h2>
        <p>
          By registering and using the Services listed on our website you specifically consent and give your authorisation to the use and transmission/transfer/sharing of your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data or Information with us and our third-party partners, for the sole purposes of providing the Services.
        </p>
        <p>
          You may discontinue the use/transfer/transmission and sharing of any of your Sensitive Personal Data or Information at any time, by writing to our Grievance Redressal Officer at <a href="mailto:compliance@grgindia.in" class="text-[#E41E3A] hover:underline">compliance@grgindia.in</a>.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">What This Privacy Policy Covers</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>This Privacy Policy covers My Incentives' treatment of your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data or Information collected when you use any of the Services offered by us on our website.</li>
          <li>This policy does not apply to companies or entities that My Incentives does not own or control, or to people that My Incentives does not employ, engage or manage.</li>
          <li>If you choose not to provide the Personal Information or Sensitive Personal Data or Information we seek, you may not be able to avail the Services offered on our website, or we may not be able to respond to your queries.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Information Collection and Use</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>My Incentives collects Personally Identifiable Information when you register, either through the website or through the mobile application.</li>
          <li>When you register, we ask for your full name, email address, mobile/telephone number, birth date, location/address, gender, occupation, industry and any other information necessary to effectively offer the Services.</li>
          <li>My Incentives also automatically receives and records information on our server logs from your browser including your IP address, cookie information and the webpage you have requested to view.</li>
          <li>We use your Personally Identifiable Information to fulfil your requests for services, and to contact you about special offers and new services.</li>
          <li>We may also use your information for purposes such as redeeming gift vouchers, auditing, data analysis and research to improve our offerings.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Information Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
        <p>My Incentives will not sell or rent your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data or Information to anyone. We will only share such information in the following cases:</p>
        <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>For the purpose of providing the Services</li>
          <li>Upon requests from any Indian or foreign government, security agencies, law enforcement agencies, or any other statutory or regulatory agencies under the law in force in India</li>
          <li>To respond to court summons, court orders or legal process</li>
          <li>If we believe it is necessary to investigate, prevent, or take action regarding illegal activities, suspected fraud, situations involving potential threats to the physical safety of any person, or as otherwise required by law</li>
          <li>If My Incentives is acquired by or merged with another company, in which case we will notify you before your information is transferred</li>
          <li>If you have violated the My Incentives Terms of Use</li>
        </ol>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Non-Personal Information</h2>
        <p>We may collect, use, transfer, and disclose non-personal information for any purpose, including:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>Information such as occupation, language, zip code, area code, unique device identifier, referrer URL, and location to better understand customer behaviour and improve our products and services</li>
          <li>Information regarding customer activities on our website, aggregated to help us understand which parts of our website are of most interest</li>
          <li>Details of how you use the Services, including search queries, to improve the relevancy of results</li>
        </ul>
        <p>If we combine non-personal information with Personally Identifiable Information, the combined information will be treated as Personally Identifiable Information for as long as it remains combined.</p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Cookies</h2>
        <p>
          My Incentives may set and access cookies on your computer. We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies (with your consent) to understand how our website is used. You can manage your cookie preferences at any time using the cookie consent banner on our website.
        </p>
        <p>
          Other companies presenting advertisements on our web pages may set and access their own cookies on your computer. Their use of cookies is subject to their own privacy policies.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Your Rights</h2>
        <p>
          My Incentives gives you the ability to edit the information that is logged when you register on our website, and your preferences at any time, including whether you want My Incentives to contact you about offers and new services.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Security</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
          <li>My Incentives stores all your Personally Identifiable Information and Sensitive Personal Data on secure servers.</li>
          <li>In certain areas, we use industry-standard encryption to protect data transmissions.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          My Incentives may amend this Privacy Policy from time to time. If we make any substantial changes in the way we use your Personally Identifiable Information, we will notify you by posting a prominent announcement on the website.
        </p>

        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#0f1f3d] mt-10">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          For any questions or concerns regarding this Privacy Policy, or to exercise your rights regarding your personal data, please contact our Grievance Redressal Officer at <a href="mailto:compliance@grgindia.in" class="text-[#E41E3A] hover:underline">compliance@grgindia.in</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
